Description: Collective Context Commander - Multi-Agent AI Orchestration
 CCC Commander (cccmd) provides pragmatic multi-agent AI orchestration
 for the Collective Context ecosystem. It enables seamless coordination
 between multiple AI agents, session persistence, and supports 300+ AI
 models through various providers.